        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/marrakesh/_scene_spider.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository e450889e-1e00-42bf-937f-6b1520af01a7).Image",
        "Description": "47,\r\rI&apos;m so tired of hearing this stupid shopkeep&apos;s dialogue every single time you pass by her. SNAIL MEAT! SNAIL MEAT! NO BONES! Like girl we get it. Please take her out in the same way she does her snails: A clean saber to the gut. Oh, and please keep this on the low. This isn&apos;t &quot;technically&quot; a &quot;real contract from the ICA.&quot; I just really can&apos;t stand to hear her say that line again.\r\rThanks. \r- Diana.",
